# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# 1) Canonicalize www to bare domain (301).
# 2) SPA fallback: serve /index.html for any unmatched path so the React
#    Router can take over for client-side navigation. Cloudflare Pages
#    serves real per-route static files (dist/<route>/index.html) for
#    direct hits before falling back here.
https://www.queencitypreciousmetals.com/* https://queencitypreciousmetals.com/:splat 301!
